gram\": \"The cycling star\", \"from\": 168, \"to\": 184}, {\"ngram\": \"silvers\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 196}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual sprint\", \"from\": 200, \"to\": 221}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 262}, {\"ngram\": \"sprint\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 269}, {\"ngram\": \"theParisOlympics\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"teammates\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 335}, {\"ngram\": \"his intention\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"nationalityand ride\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson was born in Maidstone, England and moved toAustraliaat the age of nine but has faced huge criticism for the decision, most notably from former Commonwealth champion Katherine Bates.\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 429, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9998525801841412, \"rank\": 0.00014744155134383772, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 463, \"end\": 470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.779142016234284, \"rank\": 0.21516710335728534, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999996705355, \"rank\": 3.1307856753282206e-10, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 605, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Bates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katherine Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Bates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine_Bates\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Maidstone\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"toAustraliaat\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"huge criticism\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is a lot of people who just can not believe it and some who are feeling, personally, quite let down because they were blindsided by it,' Bates said.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\", \"score\": 0.9998685039077222, \"rank\": 0.00013116239773464626, \"text\": \"Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 638}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Others who are feeling a little bit ripped off because supporting him over the years has come at the direct cost of supporting other athletes.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Others\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 787}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"the direct cost\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think the tie to your country is very strong but, in saying that, if there is that tie, then I am not really sure why he would not have made this leap years ago.'\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tie\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"your country\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"that tie\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"this leap\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Richardson, who is in a relationship with Team GB cycling star Emma Finucane, has now addressed his controversial and said he feels no remorse over the decision.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9998525801841412, \"rank\": 0.00014744155134383772, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9945452166575438, \"rank\": 0.005056478438465435, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"score\": 0.9995796654043068, \"rank\": 0.00026754067537522767, \"text\": \"Emma\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a relationship\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"his controversial\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"no remorse\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1243}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I obviously understood that there would be a bit of bitterness around this decision, but at the end of the day it's my career and it's my life,' he toldABC News.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"bitterness\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"this decision\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"' he toldABC News\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Everyone's entitled to their opinion.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"their opinion\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's up to me whether I want to listen to it or not, and I have obviously chosen not to.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's a free world, and they can do and say what they like.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a free world\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am happy with the decision I have made.'\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Responding directing to Bates' suggestion that Australian cycling had been 'ripped off' by his departure, the 25-year-old said: 'The investment that was put into me over the last few years in Australian cycling, I feel like I made a good return on that investment, winning two silver medals and a bronze medal at the Olympic Games for Australia.'\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 2007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1685, \"end\": 1690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\", \"score\": 0.9998685039077222, \"rank\": 0.00013116239773464626, \"text\": \"Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \